and $char's VehVeh's know is true
and $char's VehVeh's location is $place's sublocation and it is "Apesai Lighthouse"
and $char's VehVeh's opinion's 2nd > 20
and $char's VehVeh's arc is 1
)

(metadata:
"NPC", "VehVeh",
